aw State Owls football team|Kennesaw State]]'''\n| RD1-score14='''28'''\n| RD1-seed13=&nbsp;\n| RD1-seed14=&nbsp;\n\n| RD1-team15 ={{nowrap|'''[[2019 Southeastern Louisiana Lions football team|Southeastern Louisiana]]'''}}\n| RD1-score15= '''45'''\n| RD1-team16 =[[2019 Villanova Wildcats football team|Villanova]]\n| RD1-score16= 44\n| RD1-seed15=&nbsp;\n| RD1-seed16=&nbsp;\n\n<!-- second round (teams 1 through 8 are seeded by the NCAA) -->\n| RD2-seed1 = 1 \n| RD2-team1 = '''[[2019 North Dakota State Bison football team|North Dakota State]]'''\n| RD2-score1= '''37'''\n| RD2-team2 = Nicholls\n| RD2-score2= 13\n\n| RD2-seed3 = 8 \n| RD2-team3 = [[2019 Central Arkansas Bears football team|Central Arkansas]]\n| RD2-score3= 14\n| RD2-team4 ='''Illinois State'''\n| RD2-score4= '''24'''\n\n| RD2-seed5 = 4 \n| RD2-team5 = [[2019 Sacramento State Hornets football team|Sacramento State]]\n| RD2-score5= 28\n| RD2-team6 = '''Austin Peay'''\n| RD2-score6= '''42'''\n\n| RD2-seed7 = 5\n| RD2-team7 = '''[[2019 Montana State Bobcats football team|Montana State]]'''\n| RD2-score7= '''47'''\n| RD2-team8 = Albany\n| RD2-score8= 21\n\n| RD2-seed9  = 2 \n| RD2-team9  = '''[[2019 James Madison Dukes football team|James Madison]]'''\n| RD2-score9 = '''66'''\n| RD2-team10 = Monmouth\n| RD2-score10= 21\n\n| RD2-seed11 = 7 \n| RD2-team11 = [[2019 South Dakota State Jackrabbits football team|South Dakota State]]\n| RD2-score11= 10\n| RD2-team12 = '''Northern Iowa'''\n| RD2-score12= '''13'''\n\n| RD2-seed13 = 3 \n| RD2-team13 = '''[[2019 Weber State Wildcats football team|Weber State]]'''\n| RD2-score13= '''26'''\n| RD2-team14 = Kennesaw State\n| RD2-score14= 20\n\n| RD2-seed15 = 6 \n| RD2-team15 = '''[[2019 Montana Grizzlies football team|Montana]]'''\n| RD2-score15= '''73'''\n| RD2-team16 = {{nowrap|Southeastern Louisiana}}\n| RD2-score16= 28\n\n<!-- Quarterfinals -->\n| RD3-seed1 =1\n| RD3-team1 = '''North Dakota State'''\n| RD3-score1='''9'''\n| RD3-team2 = Illinois State\n| RD3-score2=3\n\